import { AiOutlinePlusCircle, AiOutlineLogout, AiFillStar, AiOutlineHistory, AiOutlineUser, AiOutlineFieldTime } from 'react-icons/ai'
import { FaHome } from "react-icons/fa";
import { GrNext, GrStar, GrLinkNext, GrLinkPrevious } from 'react-icons/gr'
import { BsChevronRight, BsBookmarkStarFill, BsChevronDown, BsCameraFill, BsStopwatch, BsHash, BsDot, BsTelephoneFill } from 'react-icons/bs'
import { HiOutlineLocationMarker, HiLocationMarker, HiUserGroup } from 'react-icons/hi'
import { TbReportMoney, TbLayoutDashboard } from 'react-icons/tb'
import { RiCrop2Line, RiHeartFill, RiHeartLine, RiSendPlaneFill } from 'react-icons/ri'
import { MdOutlineHouseSiding, MdOutlineLibraryBooks, MdOutlineGroups, MdOutlineReportGmailerrorred, MdReportProblem, MdPersonAddAlt1, MdOutlinePostAdd } from 'react-icons/md'
import { FiSearch } from 'react-icons/fi'
import { ImPencil2, ImBin } from 'react-icons/im'
import { BiUserPin } from 'react-icons/bi'
import { SiZalo } from 'react-icons/si'
import { FaComments } from 'react-icons/fa'

const icons = {
    FaHome,
    AiOutlinePlusCircle,
    GrNext,
    BsChevronRight,
    HiOutlineLocationMarker,
    TbReportMoney,
    RiCrop2Line,
    MdOutlineHouseSiding,
    FiSearch,
    GrStar,
    RiHeartFill,
    RiHeartLine,
    BsBookmarkStarFill,
    GrLinkNext,
    GrLinkPrevious,
    ImPencil2,
    MdOutlineLibraryBooks,
    BiUserPin,
    AiOutlineLogout,
    BsChevronDown,
    ImBin,
    BsCameraFill,
    HiLocationMarker,
    BsStopwatch,
    BsHash,
    BsDot,
    BsTelephoneFill,
    SiZalo,
    AiFillStar,
    RiSendPlaneFill,
    AiOutlineHistory,
    FaComments,
    TbLayoutDashboard,
    AiOutlineUser,
    MdOutlineGroups,
    MdOutlineReportGmailerrorred,
    AiOutlineFieldTime,
    MdReportProblem,
    HiUserGroup, MdPersonAddAlt1, MdOutlinePostAdd
}

export default icons
